### Joshua Harrison
I am a software engineer for Google. I work on Google Maps.

### Wiki

I set up a Wiki, mainly to track processes as I go about developing. It's always a pain coming back to a technology some time later and having to spend time re-finding all the tutorials and pages that were so useful in getting things set up right for the first time.

[husafan.github.io Wiki](https://github.com/husafan/husafan.github.io/wiki)
